      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LITTLE BIT SUPER (3) jumped quickly from box four to score (22.57) two back then drew the same last time but settled off pace and could manage only a 13 length 8th at The Gardens (23.69). Has claims if she runs up to expectations. MAGIC WYLDE (1) jumped well and was a winner (22.60) two back from a tricky draw then last start drew a squeeze box again but got further back and finished 5th at this track (23.06). Should be thereabouts. FREIGHT EXPRESS (8) goes very well this course and distance starting 18 times for seven wins and four minors. Placed last time (22.58) at this track in a NG, finishing second and beaten 8 lengths. Looks a key chance on best figures. KAWASAKI GIRL (2) can feature with the right run.",
